{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1055,"text":"It's an amazing thing"},{"time":2230,"text":"that we're here to talk\nabout the year of patients rising."},{"time":7006,"text":"You heard stories earlier today"},{"time":8750,"text":"about patients who are taking\ncontrol of their cases,"},{"time":11802,"text":"patients who are saying,"},{"time":12981,"text":"\"You know what, I know what the odds are,"},{"time":14979,"text":"but I'm going to look\nfor more information."},{"time":17153,"text":"I'm going to define\nwhat the terms of my success are.\""},{"time":20937,"text":"I'm going to be sharing with you\nhow, four years ago, I almost died --"},{"time":24750,"text":"found out I was, in fact,\nalready almost dead --"},{"time":27657,"text":"and what I then found out"},{"time":29919,"text":"about what's called\nthe e-Patient movement."},{"time":32145,"text":"I'll explain what that term means."},{"time":33818,"text":"I had been blogging\nunder the name \"Patient Dave,\""},{"time":36610,"text":"and when I discovered this,"},{"time":38008,"text":"I just renamed myself e-Patient Dave."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40679,"text":"Regarding the word \"patient\":"},{"time":42406,"text":"When I first started a few years ago\ngetting involved in health care"},{"time":46366,"text":"and attending meetings\nas just a casual observer,"},{"time":48750,"text":"I noticed that people\nwould talk about patients"},{"time":51013,"text":"as if it was somebody\nwho's not in the room here --"},{"time":53612,"text":"somebody out there."},{"time":55030,"text":"Some of our talks today,\nwe still act like that."},{"time":57567,"text":"But I'm here to tell you:"},{"time":59503,"text":"\"patient\" is not a third-person word."},{"time":62885,"text":"All right?"},{"time":64072,"text":"You yourself will find\nyourself in a hospital bed --"},{"time":67316,"text":"or your mother, your child --"},{"time":68995,"text":"there are heads nodding, people who say,"},{"time":70937,"text":"\"Yes, I know exactly what you mean.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":72702,"text":"So when you hear what I'm going\nto talk about here today,"},{"time":75750,"text":"first of all, I want to say that I am here"},{"time":78804,"text":"on behalf of all the patients\nthat I have ever met,"},{"time":81408,"text":"all the ones I haven't met."},{"time":83135,"text":"This is about letting patients\nplay a more active role"},{"time":86932,"text":"in helping health care,\nin fixing health care."},{"time":89933,"text":"One of the senior doctors at my hospital,"},{"time":91956,"text":"Charlie Safran,\nand his colleague, Warner Slack,"},{"time":94554,"text":"have been saying for decades"},{"time":96096,"text":"that the most underutilized\nresource in all of health care"},{"time":99880,"text":"is the patient."},{"time":101599,"text":"They have been saying that\nsince the 1970s."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104289,"text":"Now, I'm going to step back in history."},{"time":106269,"text":"This is from July, 1969."},{"time":108179,"text":"I was a freshman in college,"},{"time":109865,"text":"and this was when we first\nlanded on the Moon."},{"time":112853,"text":"And it was the first time"},{"time":114308,"text":"we had ever seen from another surface --"},{"time":117095,"text":"that's the place\nwhere you and I are right now,"},{"time":119363,"text":"where we live."},{"time":120545,"text":"The world was changing."},{"time":122116,"text":"It was about to change\nin ways that nobody could foresee."},{"time":125117,"text":"A few weeks later, Woodstock happened."},{"time":129385,"text":"Three days of fun and music."},{"time":131489,"text":"Here, just for historical authenticity,"},{"time":133613,"text":"is a picture of me in that year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135436,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":138686,"text":"Yeah, the wavy hair, the blue eyes --"},{"time":140687,"text":"it was really something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142350,"text":"That fall of 1969,"},{"time":144351,"text":"the Whole Earth Catalog came out."},{"time":146262,"text":"It was a hippie journal\nof self-sufficiency."},{"time":149750,"text":"We think of hippies\nof being just hedonists,"},{"time":152805,"text":"but there's a very strong component --\nI was in that movement --"},{"time":156030,"text":"a very strong component\nof being responsible for yourself."},{"time":159398,"text":"This book's title's subtitle\nis \"Access to Tools.\""},{"time":163319,"text":"It talked about how to build\nyour own house,"},{"time":165639,"text":"how to grow your own food,\nall kinds of things."},{"time":168068,"text":"In the 1980s,"},{"time":169496,"text":"this young doctor, Tom Ferguson,"},{"time":171654,"text":"was the medical editor\nof the Whole Earth Catalog."},{"time":174305,"text":"He saw that the great majority\nof what we do in medicine and health care"},{"time":179100,"text":"is taking care of ourselves."},{"time":181011,"text":"In fact, he said it was 70 to 80 percent"},{"time":183386,"text":"of how we actually\ntake care of our bodies."},{"time":185679,"text":"Well, he also saw that when health care\nturns to medical care"},{"time":190381,"text":"because of a more serious disease,"},{"time":192315,"text":"the key thing that holds us back\nis access to information."},{"time":195663,"text":"And when the Web came along,\nthat changed everything,"},{"time":198953,"text":"because not only\ncould we find information,"},{"time":201570,"text":"we could find other people like ourselves"},{"time":204310,"text":"who could gather,\nwho could bring us information."},{"time":206925,"text":"And he coined this term \"e-Patients\" --"},{"time":209464,"text":"equipped, engaged, empowered, enabled."},{"time":211819,"text":"Obviously, at this stage of life"},{"time":213544,"text":"he was in a somewhat more dignified\nform than he was back then."}]},{"cues":[{"time":217535,"text":"Now, I was an engaged patient\nlong before I ever heard of the term."},{"time":221513,"text":"In 2006, I went to my doctor\nfor a regular physical,"},{"time":224513,"text":"and I had said, \"I have a sore shoulder.\""},{"time":226836,"text":"Well, I got an X-ray,"},{"time":228433,"text":"and the next morning --"},{"time":230105,"text":"you may have noticed, those of you\nwho have been through a medical crisis"},{"time":233654,"text":"will understand this."},{"time":234878,"text":"This morning, some of the speakers\nnamed the date when they found out"},{"time":239364,"text":"about their condition."},{"time":240659,"text":"For me, it was 9am"},{"time":243096,"text":"on January 3, 2007."},{"time":245824,"text":"I was at the office; my desk was clean."},{"time":248343,"text":"I had the blue partition\ncarpet on the walls."},{"time":252087,"text":"The phone rang and it was my doctor."},{"time":254907,"text":"He said, \"Dave, I pulled\nup the X-ray image"},{"time":257750,"text":"on the screen on the computer at home.\""},{"time":259864,"text":"He said, \"Your shoulder\nis going to be fine,"},{"time":261955,"text":"but Dave, there's something in your lung.\""},{"time":264064,"text":"And if you look in that red oval,"},{"time":265996,"text":"that shadow was not supposed to be there."},{"time":269750,"text":"To make a long story short,"},{"time":271750,"text":"I said, \"So you need me\nto get back in there?\""},{"time":273929,"text":"He said, \"Yeah, we're going to need\nto do a CT scan of your chest.\""},{"time":277204,"text":"In parting, I said,\n\"Is there anything I should do?\""},{"time":279869,"text":"He said -- think about this one,"},{"time":281750,"text":"this is the advice your doctor gives you:"},{"time":283750,"text":"\"Just go home and have a glass\nof wine with your wife.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":289023,"text":"I went in for the CAT scan."},{"time":292218,"text":"It turns out there were\nfive of these things in both my lungs."},{"time":295469,"text":"So at that point we knew\nthat it was cancer."},{"time":297655,"text":"We knew it wasn't lung cancer."},{"time":299718,"text":"That meant it was metastasized\nfrom somewhere."},{"time":303128,"text":"The question was, where from?"},{"time":305234,"text":"So I went in for an ultrasound."},{"time":307884,"text":"I got to do what many women have --"},{"time":310401,"text":"the jelly on the belly and the, \"Bzzzz!\""},{"time":313750,"text":"My wife came with me."},{"time":315935,"text":"She's a veterinarian,"},{"time":317564,"text":"so she's seen lots of ultrasounds."},{"time":319385,"text":"I mean, she knows I'm not a dog."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320993,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":322661,"text":"This is an MRI image."},{"time":325662,"text":"This is much sharper\nthan an ultrasound would be."},{"time":328108,"text":"What we saw in that kidney"},{"time":330882,"text":"was that big blob there."},{"time":332417,"text":"There were actually two of these:\none was growing out the front"},{"time":335481,"text":"and had already erupted\nand latched onto the bowel."},{"time":337928,"text":"One was growing out the back\nand it attached to the psoas muscle,"},{"time":341171,"text":"which is a big muscle in the back\nthat I'd never heard of,"},{"time":343980,"text":"but all of a sudden I cared about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345837,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":346860,"text":"I went home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":348047,"text":"Now, I've been Googling --"},{"time":349345,"text":"I've been online since 1989,\non CompuServe."},{"time":351759,"text":"I went home, and I know\nyou can't read the details here;"},{"time":354413,"text":"that's not important."},{"time":355603,"text":"My point is, I went to a respected\nmedical website, WebMD,"},{"time":359831,"text":"because I know how to filter out junk."},{"time":362113,"text":"I also found my wife online."},{"time":364638,"text":"Before I met her,"},{"time":366344,"text":"I went through some suboptimal\nsearch results."}]},{"cues":[{"time":368844,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":370416,"text":"So I looked for quality information."},{"time":373594,"text":"There's so much about trust --"},{"time":375350,"text":"what sources of information can we trust?"},{"time":377877,"text":"Where does my body end\nand an invader start?"},{"time":382665,"text":"A cancer, a tumor, is something\nyou grow out of your own tissue."},{"time":385827,"text":"How does that happen?"},{"time":387416,"text":"Where does medical ability end and start?"},{"time":391459,"text":"Well, so what I read on WebMD:"},{"time":393915,"text":"\"The prognosis is poor\nfor progressing renal cell cancer."},{"time":398925,"text":"Almost all patients are incurable.\""},{"time":402307,"text":"I've been online long enough to know\nif I don't like the first results I get,"},{"time":406046,"text":"I go look for more."},{"time":407223,"text":"And what I found on other websites was,"},{"time":409909,"text":"even by the third page of Google results:"},{"time":412297,"text":"\"Outlook is bleak.\""},{"time":414352,"text":"\"Prognosis is grim.\""},{"time":416939,"text":"And I'm thinking, \"What the heck?\""},{"time":419059,"text":"I didn't feel sick at all."},{"time":420815,"text":"I mean, I'd been getting\ntired in the evening,"},{"time":423029,"text":"but I was 56 years old, you know?"},{"time":425069,"text":"I was slowly losing weight,"},{"time":426750,"text":"but for me, that was what\nthe doctor told me to do."},{"time":430998,"text":"It was really something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":432694,"text":"And this is the diagram\nof stage 4 kidney cancer"},{"time":435898,"text":"from the drug I eventually got."},{"time":437679,"text":"Totally by coincidence,\nthere's that thing in my lung."},{"time":440749,"text":"In the left femur, the left thigh bone,\nthere's another one."},{"time":443750,"text":"I had one. My leg eventually snapped."},{"time":446139,"text":"I fainted and landed on it, and it broke."},{"time":449085,"text":"There's one in the skull,"},{"time":450357,"text":"and then for good measure,\nI had these other tumors,"},{"time":452844,"text":"including, by the time\nmy treatment started,"},{"time":454939,"text":"one was growing out of my tongue."},{"time":456552,"text":"I had kidney cancer\ngrowing out of my tongue."},{"time":458720,"text":"And what I read"},{"time":459903,"text":"was that my median survival was 24 weeks."},{"time":463164,"text":"This was bad."},{"time":464643,"text":"I was facing the grave."},{"time":467043,"text":"I thought, \"What's my mother's face\ngoing to look like"},{"time":469641,"text":"on the day of my funeral?\""},{"time":471345,"text":"I had to sit down with my daughter\nand say, \"Here's the situation.\""},{"time":476854,"text":"Her boyfriend was with her."},{"time":478292,"text":"I said, \"I don't want you guys\nto get married prematurely,"},{"time":481117,"text":"just so you can do it\nwhile Dad's still alive.\""},{"time":485079,"text":"It's really serious."},{"time":486672,"text":"If you wonder why patients\nare motivated and want to help,"},{"time":490276,"text":"think about this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491458,"text":"Well, my doctor prescribed\na patient community, ACOR.org,"},{"time":495512,"text":"a network of cancer patients,\nof all amazing things."},{"time":498750,"text":"Very quickly they told me,"},{"time":500750,"text":"\"Kidney cancer is an uncommon disease."},{"time":502750,"text":"Get yourself to a specialist center."},{"time":504751,"text":"There is no cure, but there's something\nthat sometimes works --"},{"time":507774,"text":"it usually doesn't --"},{"time":509354,"text":"called high-dosage interleukin."},{"time":511192,"text":"Most hospitals don't offer it,"},{"time":513224,"text":"so they won't even tell you it exists."},{"time":515423,"text":"Don't let them give you\nanything else first."},{"time":517566,"text":"And by the way, here are four doctors\nin your part of the United States"},{"time":520963,"text":"who offer it, and their phone numbers.\""},{"time":522938,"text":"How amazing is that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":525400,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":528238,"text":"Here's the thing:"},{"time":529458,"text":"Here we are, four years later --"},{"time":531070,"text":"you can't find a website\nthat gives patients that information."},{"time":534670,"text":"Government-approved,\nAmerican Cancer Society,"},{"time":537227,"text":"but patients know\nwhat patients want to know."},{"time":540834,"text":"It's the power of patient networks."},{"time":543629,"text":"This amazing substance --\nagain, I mentioned:"},{"time":546882,"text":"Where does my body end?"},{"time":548260,"text":"My oncologist and I talk a lot these days"},{"time":550678,"text":"because I try to keep my talks\ntechnically accurate."},{"time":553203,"text":"And he said, \"You know, the immune\nsystem is good at detecting invaders,"},{"time":558277,"text":"bacteria coming from outside,"},{"time":560618,"text":"but when it's your own tissue\nthat you've grown,"},{"time":563116,"text":"it's a whole different thing.\""},{"time":564659,"text":"And I went through\na mental exercise, actually,"},{"time":567639,"text":"because I started a patient support\ncommunity of my own on a website,"},{"time":572481,"text":"and one of my friends --\none of my relatives, actually -- said,"},{"time":575539,"text":"\"Look, Dave, who grew this thing?"},{"time":578894,"text":"Are you going to set yourself up\nas mentally attacking yourself?\""},{"time":582941,"text":"So we went into it."},{"time":584569,"text":"The story of how all that\nhappened is in the book."}]},{"cues":[{"time":587310,"text":"Anyway, this is the way\nthe numbers unfolded."},{"time":589758,"text":"Me being me, I put the numbers\nfrom my hospital's website,"},{"time":592913,"text":"for my tumor sizes,"},{"time":594096,"text":"into a spreadsheet."},{"time":595271,"text":"Don't worry about the numbers."},{"time":596750,"text":"You see, that's the immune system."},{"time":598526,"text":"Amazing thing, those two yellow lines"},{"time":600527,"text":"are where I got the two doses\nof interleukin two months apart."},{"time":604750,"text":"And look at how the tumor sizes\nplummeted in between."},{"time":607904,"text":"Just incredible."},{"time":609387,"text":"Who knows what we'll be able to do\nwhen we learn to make more use of it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":612841,"text":"The punch line is that a year\nand a half later,"},{"time":615181,"text":"I was there when this magnificent\nyoung woman, my daughter,"},{"time":619505,"text":"got married."},{"time":620692,"text":"And when she came down those steps,"},{"time":623091,"text":"and it was just her and me\nfor that moment,"},{"time":625345,"text":"I was so glad that she didn't have\nto say to her mother,"},{"time":628591,"text":"\"I wish Dad could have been here.\""},{"time":630671,"text":"And this is what we're doing\nwhen we make health care better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":634575,"text":"Now, I want to talk briefly\nabout a couple of other patients"},{"time":637502,"text":"who are doing everything\nin their power to improve health care."},{"time":640535,"text":"This is Regina Holliday,"},{"time":642198,"text":"a painter in Washington DC,\nwhose husband died of kidney cancer"},{"time":646421,"text":"a year after my disease."},{"time":647945,"text":"She's painting, here, a mural"},{"time":649750,"text":"of his horrible\nfinal weeks in the hospital."},{"time":652750,"text":"One of the things that she discovered"},{"time":655221,"text":"was that her husband's medical record\nin this paper folder"},{"time":659529,"text":"was just disorganized."},{"time":661079,"text":"And she thought, \"You know,\nif I have a nutrition facts label"},{"time":664368,"text":"on the side of a cereal box,"},{"time":666115,"text":"why can't there be something that simple"},{"time":668094,"text":"telling every new nurse who comes on duty,"},{"time":670662,"text":"every new doctor,"},{"time":671911,"text":"the basics about my husband's condition?\""},{"time":674045,"text":"So she painted this medical facts mural\nwith a nutrition label,"},{"time":679345,"text":"something like that,"},{"time":680526,"text":"in a diagram of him."},{"time":681750,"text":"She then, last year, painted this diagram."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684750,"text":"She studied health care like me."},{"time":686658,"text":"She came to realize\nthere were a lot of people"},{"time":689118,"text":"who'd written patient-advocate books"},{"time":691152,"text":"that you just don't hear\nabout at medical conferences."},{"time":694019,"text":"Patients are such\nan underutilized resource."},{"time":697679,"text":"Well, as it said in my introduction,"},{"time":699428,"text":"I've gotten somewhat known for saying"},{"time":701234,"text":"that patients should have\naccess to their data."},{"time":703465,"text":"I actually said at one conference\na couple of years ago,"},{"time":706165,"text":"\"Give me my damn data,"},{"time":707352,"text":"because you people\ncan't be trusted to keep it clean.\""},{"time":709979,"text":"And here, she has our \"damned\" data --"},{"time":712750,"text":"it's a pun --"},{"time":714068,"text":"which is starting to break out,\nstarting to break through --"},{"time":717020,"text":"the water symbolizes our data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":719140,"text":"And in fact,"},{"time":720315,"text":"I want to do a little something\nimprovisational for you."},{"time":723043,"text":"There's a guy on Twitter that I know,\na health IT guy outside Boston,"},{"time":726936,"text":"and he wrote the e-Patient rap."},{"time":729492,"text":"And it goes like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":731214,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":732856,"text":"(Beatboxing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":736940,"text":"(Rapping) Gimme my damn data"},{"time":738989,"text":"I wanna be an e-Patient just like Dave"},{"time":741481,"text":"Gimme my damn data,\n'cause it's my life to save"},{"time":744041,"text":"(Normal voice) Now, I'm not going\nto go any further --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":746643,"text":"(Applause) (Cheering)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":761005,"text":"Well, thank you. That shot the timing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":763434,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":765099,"text":"Think about the possibility."},{"time":766594,"text":"Why is it that iPhones and iPads\nadvance far faster"},{"time":771004,"text":"than the health tools\nthat are available to you"},{"time":773268,"text":"to help take care of your family?"},{"time":775520,"text":"Here's a website, VisibleBody.com,\nthat I stumbled across."},{"time":779664,"text":"And I thought, \"You know,\nI wonder what my psoas muscle is?\""},{"time":782622,"text":"So you can click on things and remove it."},{"time":784623,"text":"And I saw, \"Aha! That's the kidney\nand the psoas muscle.\""},{"time":787624,"text":"I was rotating it in 3D\nand saying, \"I understand now.\""},{"time":791609,"text":"And then I realized\nit reminded me of Google Earth,"},{"time":794568,"text":"where you can fly to any address."},{"time":797345,"text":"And I thought, \"Why not take this\nand connect it to my digital scan data"},{"time":802697,"text":"and have Google Earth for my body?\""},{"time":805606,"text":"What did Google come out with this year?"},{"time":807750,"text":"Now there's Google Body browser."},{"time":810358,"text":"But you see, it's still generic."},{"time":812359,"text":"It's not my data."},{"time":814263,"text":"But if we can get that data\nout from behind the dam"},{"time":817361,"text":"so software innovators can pounce on it"},{"time":820362,"text":"the way software innovators like to do,"},{"time":822662,"text":"who knows what we'll be able\nto come up with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":824872,"text":"One final story."},{"time":826047,"text":"This is Kelly Young, a rheumatoid\narthritis patient from Florida."},{"time":830998,"text":"This is a live story,\nunfolding just in the last few weeks."},{"time":834541,"text":"RA patients, as they call themselves --\nher blog is \"RA Warrior\" --"},{"time":840109,"text":"have a big problem,"},{"time":841490,"text":"because 40 percent of them\nhave no visible symptoms."},{"time":844750,"text":"And that makes it really hard\nto tell how the disease is going,"},{"time":847832,"text":"and some doctors think,\n\"Yeah right, you're really in pain.\""},{"time":851013,"text":"Well, she found,\nthrough her online research,"},{"time":853750,"text":"a nuclear bone scan\nthat's usually used for cancer,"},{"time":857162,"text":"but it can also reveal inflammation."},{"time":859975,"text":"And she saw that\nif there is no inflammation,"},{"time":863909,"text":"then the scan is a uniform gray."},{"time":866393,"text":"So she took it."},{"time":867612,"text":"And the radiologist's report\nsaid, \"No cancer found.\""},{"time":871917,"text":"Well, that's not what\nhe was supposed to do with it."},{"time":874420,"text":"So she wanted to have it read again,"},{"time":876865,"text":"and her doctor fired her."},{"time":878750,"text":"She pulled up the CD."},{"time":880657,"text":"He said, \"If you don't want to follow\nmy instructions, go away.\""},{"time":884959,"text":"So she pulled up the CD\nof the scan images,"},{"time":887750,"text":"and look at all those hot spots."},{"time":889750,"text":"And she's now actively engaged on her blog"},{"time":892750,"text":"in looking for assistance\nin getting better care."},{"time":896060,"text":"See, that is an empowered\npatient -- no medical training."}]},{"cues":[{"time":898876,"text":"We are, you are,"},{"time":900871,"text":"the most underused\nresource in health care."},{"time":903590,"text":"What she was able to do"},{"time":905130,"text":"was because she had access\nto the raw data."},{"time":907896,"text":"How big a deal was this?"},{"time":909292,"text":"Well at TED2009,"},{"time":911062,"text":"Tim Berners-Lee himself,\ninventor of the Web,"},{"time":914360,"text":"gave a talk where he said\nthe next big thing"},{"time":917361,"text":"is not to have your browser find\nother people's articles about the data,"},{"time":922060,"text":"but the raw data."},{"time":923266,"text":"And he got them chanting\nby the end of the talk,"},{"time":926060,"text":"\"Raw data now! Raw data now!\""},{"time":929751,"text":"And I ask you,"},{"time":931289,"text":"three words, please,\nto improve health care:"},{"time":934567,"text":"Let patients help!"},{"time":936568,"text":"Let patients help!"},{"time":938306,"text":"Let patients help!"},{"time":940185,"text":"Let patients help!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":942127,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":943415,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":960162,"text":"For all the patients around the world\nwatching this on the Webcast,"},{"time":965572,"text":"God bless you, everyone.\nLet patients help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":967917,"text":"Host: And bless yourself.\nThank you very much."}]}]}